The '''Imperial Institute of Higher Studies''' was situated on the planet [[Ferrhast]] and was known as one of the premier learning facilities during the [[New Order/Legends|New Order]]. This establishment gave students the opportunity to study all range of topics under, of course, the tight observation of [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Professor/Legends|professors]]. This control of academic education was just one aspect of the basis of Imperial mind conditioning. Pro-Imperial attitudes were supported and rewarded during these studies and any anti-regime ideas were observed, controlled, and, if necessary, wiped out.

